gn data like diameter(ID or OD) length, number of legs, type of legs etc. w=
hich can be then used in Inventor ilogic to instantly get a 3D file. Since =
we have additional tabs for the internals like coil and baffle already set =
in, can we use the same AI tool to fulfil this requirement as well?
